OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FFairly
OL,6,Fcloudy though largely dry Wednesday,
OL,7,Fsome sunshine developing later. Breezy
OL,8,Fbut bright or sunny and largely dry
OL,9,FThursday. Dry and sunny Friday.
OL,10,FTemperatures rising, becoming very
OL,11,Fwarm.
